==========
RADARE GUI
==========

* Written in Vala
* Using GTK

Uses threads
  r_core_thread


Widgets we need to do:

* Hexadecimal viewer
  - should support editing
  - text selection
* Disassembly treeview
  - Supports folding of code

+-----------------------------------------------------+
| radare-gui                                      -ox |
+-----------------------------------------------------+
|_File___Edit_________________________________________|
|  _________  |         \--------.--------.           |
| |_________| |  tabs    |_______|________|__________ |
|             |                                      ||
| .-----------| .----------------------------------. ||
| |         |^| |                                  | ||
| | flag    |-| | 0x8048000  mov eax, 0x8320       | ||
| |   list  | | | 0x8048005  push ebp              | ||
| |         | | | 0x8048006  mov ebp, esp          | ||
| |         | | | 0x8048008  sub esp, 0x20         | ||
| |         | | |__________________________________| ||
| |         | |______________________________________:|
| |         | |                                      ||
| |         |-| console                              ||
| |_________|v|---------------------------------------|
|_____________|_input prompt______________________|_>_|
|___statusbar_________________________________________|


  - tabs can be detached
  - tabs can contain graphs, code, zoomed view ...
  - code can be edited if write mode enabled
  - statusbar shows active opened file information (rwx, ..)
  - left panel provides access to flags
